{"serial": "77026", "department_serial": 63, "code": "HK4032", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Governance and Development in Hakka region", "ch": "治理與客庄發展"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liu, Hsiao-Lan"], "ch": ["劉小蘭"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "HK", "room": "210"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "客家語文暨社會科學學系", "en": "Department of Hakka Language and Social Sciences"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 12, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "工欲善其事必先利其器，古諺說明方法和工具在帶領我們邁向目標時重要性。研究工作也是如此，因此，本次課程核心著重在理論的認識理解和實作應用上，特別是透過講課和實際參訪的方式。課程內容從後進國家、國家內部次區域、社區、鄉村等各個例子的發展過程，來探討現在客庄發展與創生。在嫻熟若干方法之後，能協助同學針對主題進行多面的認識。", "en": "The course content delves into the development processes of various examples, including developing countries, sub-regions within a country, communities, and rural areas. It aims to explore the current development and revitalization of rural areas in the context of client villages. After becoming proficient in various methods, students will be able to assist in gaining a multifaceted understanding of the subject matter."}, "outline": {"ch": "課程介紹\n暖身--人為什麼而努力唸書？陳映瞳(眼科醫師)\n導論 發展研究概述：理論發展與研究方法\n第一章全球南方觀點下的國際發展與援助\n第二章國家與後進發展\n第三章國家內部次區域發展：東台灣論述與經驗\n第四章新都市：超越空間尺度的城市研究之開展\n第五章社區發展與治理創新\n第八章技術變遷：後進國家的技術學習\n第九章勞動參與：發展變遷中勞動者角色\n地方實作系列1\n地方實作系列3\n地方實作系列4\n地方實作系列5\n課程回顧與檢討\n自主學習\n自主學習", "en": "Chapter 1: International Development and Aid from a Global South Perspective\nChapter 2: States and Development in the Global South\nChapter 3: Development of Sub-National Regions within a Country: The Case of Eastern Taiwan\nChapter 4: New Urbanism: Exploring Urban Studies beyond Spatial Dimensions\nChapter 5: Community Development and Innovative Governance\nChapter 8: Technological Change: Technology